<item>
            <title>[LU-19916] start MGS replicas on MDTs/OSTs</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19916</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Start MGS replicas on MDTs/OSTs which are not located on the MGS0&lt;br/&gt;
primary and failover hosts.  And once the target which the MGS&lt;br/&gt;
replica is running on is stopped, the MGS replica will be stopped&lt;br/&gt;
as well, and it will notify the ll_cfg_requeue thread to start&lt;br/&gt;
another MGS replica on other target if possible.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Register MGS replica as observer of MGC, so that it can be notified&lt;br/&gt;
when the config is changed.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
